<HL>
   Major Railroads
   Show Strong
   Performance
   ---
   Santa Fe, Union Pacific Post
   Fourth-Quarter Profit;
   CSX Takes a Charge
   ----
   By Daniel Machalaba
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
01/23/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
